PrecisAmendments to the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE AUTHORITY REGULATIONS which relax the requirement for candidates wishing to qualify for pilotage licences and certificates to hold an NO1 certificate of competency during two of the three years watchkeeping service required, and removes the grandfathering provision for the issue of licences and certificates to person with qualifying service prior to April 10, 1974.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1995-0430 Publication Date: 1995-09-20
Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE AUTHORITY REGULATIONS which relax the
requirement for candidates wishing to qualify for pilotage licences and
certificates to hold an NO1 certificate of competency during two of the
three years watchkeeping service required, and removes the grandfathering
provision for the issue of licences and certificates to person with
qualifying service prior to April 10, 1974.
